org.efaps.db

Class Instance

  • java.lang.Object
    • org.efaps.db.Instance
  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    Serializable

    public final class Instance
extends Object
implements Serializable
    The class is used to store one object id of an instance (defined with type and id). The string representation is the type id plus point plus id.
    Version:
    $Id$
    Author:
    The eFaps Team
